title: Macklemore and Ryan Lewis head to the Louisville Palace
text:

(Photo: WHAS 11) CONNECT TWEET   
LOUISVILLE, Ky (WHAS11) -- Get ready music fans, Macklemore and Ryan Lewis are heading to the Louisville Palace. Macklemore and Ryan Lewis tickets go on sale this Friday for their January 31 show. 
The hip hop group will be bringing their best on January 31, 2016. 
Tickets will be going sale this Friday at www.LouisvillePalace.com.  //on.whas11.com/1LxfZhD More Stories
